\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Article\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"headline\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Sliding Puzzle\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Original Hard explanation for Sliding Puzzle (LeetCode #773). Pattern: a search algorithm. Time O((m * n) * (m * n)!), space O((m * n) * (m * n)!). Multi-language solutions and interview tips.\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"url\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/sliding-puzzle\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"author\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Organization\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"AlgoForge\\\\\\\"},\\\\\\\"publisher\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Organization\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"AlgoForge\\\\\\\"},\\\\\\\"datePublished\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-01-01\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"dateModified\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2026-07-17\\\\\\\"}\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$1d\\\"}}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"HowTo\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"How to solve Sliding Puzzle\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Original Hard explanation for Sliding Puzzle (LeetCode #773). Pattern: a search algorithm. Time O((m * n) * (m * n)!), space O((m * n) * (m * n)!). Multi-language solutions and interview tips.\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"step\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"HowToStep\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Read the official problem statement on LeetCode\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"HowToStep\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":2,\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Solve on paper / whiteboard first\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"HowToStep\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":3,\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Implement the a search algorithm approach\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"HowToStep\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"po