-45 transition-transform\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The reference solutions aim for O((m * n) * (m * n)!) time and O((m * n) * (m * n)!) space. Always re-derive complexity from the code you write in the interview.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What pattern does Sliding Puzzle use?\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4 group\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between gap-2\",\"children\":[\"What pattern does Sliding Puzzle use?\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-muted-foreground group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"It primarily maps to a search algorithm, within the broader topic of breadth first search.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Is Sliding Puzzle good for interviews?\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4 group\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between gap-2\",\"children\":[\"Is Sliding Puzzle good for interviews?\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-muted-foreground group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes — as a Hard problem it is a solid practice target. Pair it with related problems in the same pattern family for spaced repetition.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Where can I read the official statement?\",{\"className\":\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4 group\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between gap-2\",\"children\":[\"Where can I read the official statement?\",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-muted-foreground group-open:rotate-45 transition-tr